WEBVTT

00:03.394 --> 00:07.181
Julia, put some clothes on
around your brothers.

00:07.224 --> 00:09.009
Ryan: So, fourth date.
Gotta ask --

00:09.052 --> 00:11.011
how does the owner of a dive bar
afford a place like this?

00:11.054 --> 00:12.403
Frozen taquitos.

00:12.447 --> 00:14.884
We're gonna keep doing
the whole sexy/mysterious thing.

00:14.927 --> 00:16.451
If you want me to, sure.

00:16.494 --> 00:18.018
Mr. Cody?
Penny Dean.

00:18.061 --> 00:19.497
I'm sorry.
You're an attorney?

00:19.541 --> 00:21.543
I handle a lot of our
initial consultations, Mr. Cody.

00:21.586 --> 00:23.327
The partners here trust me --
so can you.

00:23.371 --> 00:25.547
I didn't ask for you to be
assigned to my cold-case unit.

00:25.590 --> 00:27.766
Me neither. So, what do you got?
Catherine Belen.

00:27.810 --> 00:29.420
Hi! Welcome!

00:29.464 --> 00:31.118
-Whose bike is that?
-Hey, man, I just got clean,
too.

00:31.161 --> 00:33.685
That shit's hard.
-Got to find ways
to scratch that itch.

00:33.729 --> 00:35.774
Get your asses down! Hey!
-Be ready! Let's go!

00:35.818 --> 00:38.038
-Take it easy, baby.
-Ever heard of Eddie Pham?

00:38.081 --> 00:39.822
Real flashy dude,
full of shit.

00:39.865 --> 00:42.607
This diamond guy paid 80 grand
for those just like that.

00:42.651 --> 00:45.132
-So he's just sitting on cash?
-He doesn't just sell jewelry.

00:45.175 --> 00:46.698
He makes it, too.
A lot of it.

00:46.742 --> 00:48.222
His brother knew
that the shit was cut.

00:48.265 --> 00:49.745
There's something off
between the two of them.

00:49.788 --> 00:51.355
I think we could use it.
-You really think one brother

00:51.399 --> 00:53.444
would turn on another
like that?

00:53.488 --> 00:59.146
♪♪

00:59.189 --> 01:05.065
♪♪

